text: Madeleine Steere (born 15 September 1996) is an Australian water polo player. She was part of the Australian team at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She played for the University of Michigan's women's water polo team. == References == ==Other websites== * University of Michigan's Madeleine Steere Named to Australia Stingers 2017 FINA World Championship Roster * News - Water Polo Australia * Madeleine Steere Photos Photos: Budapest 2017 FINA World Championship - Day 5 Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Australian water polo players
